So bob is kinda bummed.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Since we have been doing fairly well money wise he started looking into possibly going on a trip this year.&nbsp; He loves vegas and was looking at airfare hotel and the like for a few hours Sunday.&nbsp; He found some excellent pricing&nbsp; and was kinda jabbering on about it.&nbsp; Mortified of having to repeat the expierence i dealt with last time i flew, i suggested looking into Niagara falls instead becauwe we could drive there.. His face fell....

Bob&nbsp; &quot;Why wouldnt you want to go to Vegas&quot;
Me&nbsp; &quot; I&nbsp;dont get vacation time at work so the trip would have to be a short one.&nbsp; Niagara is much closer.&quot;
Bob&nbsp; &quot;&nbsp;You sure you cant do Vegas?&quot;
Me&nbsp; &quot;Y&quot;a id luv to see the falls&nbsp; been a dream of mine&quot;
Bob &quot; OKay i guess.&nbsp; ill see what i can find&quot;

:(&nbsp; i totally lied i didnt want to go to any place where i had to fly because last time i flew bob and i got bumped off the flight.&nbsp; When we were talking to the ticket agent making new flight arrangements she asked me if id prefer two seats to accomodate me.&nbsp; One of the other passengers behind me snorted and said... &quot;well if she doesnt take two seats i will if im next to her&quot;&nbsp; The ticket Agent gave a slight giggle.

Thats it no more flying 

Im sorry Bob.&nbsp; Im sorry im overweight and people think its a Joke.&nbsp; and most importantly im sorry i ruined your want to go to vegas because im selfconscience.

:(

i was talking to a new friend.. and he loves to hear me go on and on about things.&nbsp; He stopped me at one point saying &quot; when i hear you talk .. you have soo much you want to say it makes me think u have no one else to talk too and that makes me sad.&quot;

hes exactly right.. its not very often i got someone who is willing to digest everything i say&nbsp; i said nah i talk to lots of people.&nbsp; but.. little does he know hes probably the only person who will ask me how my day is this week.

now that im thinking about it gosh im lonely im soo glad he listens.&nbsp;&nbsp; im gonna try to talk less now haha.&nbsp; so he doesnt get that impression&nbsp; i dont want to seem desparate.
